{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Premise</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Barkley Valley, British Columbia, Canada \u2014 August 16, 2018.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thomas is trapped in a relentless struggle with sleep paralysis, haunted by inexplicable nightmares that blur the lines between dream and reality. One night, you awaken, and it\u2019s not a sleep paralysis anymore\u2014it\u2019s still your room, but something feels different. Something <strong><i>is</i></strong> different.<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941310/extras/Moonshine.gif?t=1735852628\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into Thomas\u2019 fractured psyche in this story-rich, first-person psychological horror game. Relive his horrifying episodes, piece together the mystery of his unraveling mind, and make impactful choices that will determine his fate. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941310/extras/AliceSmile.gif?t=1735852628\" /></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Narrative-Driven Experience</strong>: Immerse yourself in Thomas' story, narrated as he documents his descent into the unknown. Every revelation pulls you closer to understanding his fractured reality.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Meaningful Choices</strong>: Your decisions influence the story and shape your journey. Will you emerge stronger or spiral into chaos?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Investigative Gameplay</strong>: Gather clues from narration, notes, video tapes, and even in-game websites to piece together the enigma.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sanity Management</strong>: Fear and stress take their toll. Navigate tense scenarios carefully to keep Thomas grounded\u2014or risk losing it all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Puzzles</strong>: Solve intricate puzzles that block your path, each tied to the mysteries of Thomas\u2019 mind.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple Endings</strong>: The fate of Thomas\u2014and his sanity\u2014is in your hands. Your choices will lead to different outcomes, each reflecting your path.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique P.T.-Style Loop</strong>: Experience an original, mind-bending gameplay loop inspired by the psychological terror of <i>P.T.</i>, with a twist that ties it to Thomas\u2019 story. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1941310/extras/Prison.gif?t=1735852628\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Dolls\u2019 Story","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/24cde9492801a47efd2fd4b8fe502542f4ea87eb.jpg"},{"name":"Alice\u2019s Texts","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/e71eabcd284a4905094908d3c4d209a602ebf123.jpg"},{"name":"The Man on The Airplane","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/41afb92a65e7f1c86aaaf1f83fe035cd74f4d7bd.jpg"},{"name":"Brave But Not Brave Enough","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/cc1a4c5ba5c6321e7b6958aaad84ca6c4136dc3d.jpg"},{"name":"Prep Before Prep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/5ee4b097e57e00434a888bab28cf34fa674b17b1.jpg"},{"name":"Jane Malouin","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/2b109a5876a8f36fa055fdf170e82691ee0ef62b.jpg"},{"name":"Into The Unknown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/ca8c08748b697aaf4732976f6aef08d259de6d70.jpg"},{"name":"YEP","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1941310/cda3284ebc1a5801ef307aa79d81239a9737c49a